{"tid":1252362,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★暫緩效應？】劏房租金指數近五年最高","createTime":"2019-06-23T03:34:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T05:42:05.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8d3961bab51477aa7d7085dfb179c940233d8ead","tid":1252362,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T03:34:40.000Z","msg":"Now新聞台】有團體計算最新劏房租金指數，較去年升百分之7.7。<br />\n<br />\n全港關注劏房平台在上月及本月調查66戶居於觀塘、九龍城、葵青荃灣及深水埗的劏房戶，計算單位分間後的總租金與應課差餉租值的差距，得出今年租金指數是443，較去年上升7.7%，亦是近五年來最高。<br />\n<br />\n而平均劏房戶的租金佔收入逾四成，比去年上升4.8%，他們建議政府訂立租務管制。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=352809\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D352809&d=UYGl2U%2FUD6QdVJGaYMmpaPrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=54e0e482\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D352809&h=b5a584e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=352809</a>"},{"pid":"ed7bba98c3650c6d03f364d587a427ca80df05a0","tid":1252362,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T03:35:25.000Z","msg":"徹底破滅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SvLyiiS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSvLyiiS.jpg&h=a25883a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"011468fc16ecd07221e4282c861503931d990b46","tid":1252362,"uid":7855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T03:56:36.000Z","msg":"寧租勿買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4144b4fc583e159b80aa037ea00a74ff6277e6e","tid":1252362,"uid":9694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T05:42:05.000Z","msg":"講到口水乾個垃圾政府點會攪租金管制<br />\n班仆街食租都賺唔少"}]}